   - Unicode normalization fallback
   - Search across series folders

6. **Image Path Resolution:**
   - Absolute URLs (http/https): used as-is
   - Root paths (/): used as-is
   - Text placeholders (text:DG): used as-is
   - Relative paths (./): converted to `/posts/{slug}/...` or `/books/{slug}/...`

7. **Pagination:** All listing routes support pagination with configurable page sizes

8. **Backlinks & Slug Registry:** Built at render time, cached in production for performance

