| Page Type | Has generateMetadata | Has OG Graph | Has Twitter Card | Has Article Type | Has publishedTime |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Root layout | Static metadata | ✓ | ✓ | website | ✗ |
| Posts | `generateMetadata()` | ✓ | ✓ | **article** | ✓ |
| Series | `generateMetadata()` | ✓ | ✓ | website | ✗ |
| Books (landing) | `generateMetadata()` | ✓ | ✓ | website | ✗ |
